txt.en: The leaders of the half-orcs near Oserley roam the field south-west of the village.\n\nYou should defeat Rakblog and Unaz, leaders of the half-orc scouts near Oserley.
Defeated Rakblog
Bring the note you found to Cenulf in Oserley
Defeated Unaz

'You are mighty indeed to have faced and defeated the leaders of the half-orcs! Is there nothing you fear?

'You found a note upon one of the creatures? Let me see it....

'This is not good...not good at all....'
The leaders of the half-orcs near Oserley are particularly dangerous, attacking without hesitance any who cross their paths.
'Why have you returned so soon? Have you finished the task before you?'
Cenulf is near the mill in Oserley.\n\nYou should bring the note you found to Cenulf at once.
